article.description: — Jalen Blackmon had 17 points in Stetson's 80-59 victory over Lipscomb on Saturday.
article.headline: Blackmon's 17 lead Stetson over Lipscomb 80-59
article.story: DELAND, Fla. -- — Jalen Blackmon had 17 points in Stetson's 80-59 victory over Lipscomb on Saturday. Blackmon added seven rebounds for the Hatters (13-9, 5-2 Atlantic Sun Conference). Stephan D. Swenson scored 15 points while shooting 6 for 15 (1 for 3 from 3-point range) and 2 of 4 from the free throw line, and added seven rebounds and nine assists. Alec Oglesby was 5 of 10 shooting, including 2 for 5 from 3-point range, and went 2 for 3 from the line to finish with 14 points. Joe Anderson led the Bisons (13-9, 4-3) in scoring, finishing with nine points and three steals. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
